    ...


Django checks:

is this user allowed to add student?

âœ” 6. Secure Hashing

Django never stores passwords as plain text.

Passwords look like:

pbkdf2_sha256$320000$FJyL...


You can check this in Django admin â†’ Users table.

You never see real password â†’ only hashed.

